---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="AmicBridge – Peer-to-Peer Lending & Requests"
  description="AmicBridge is a Cyprus-based peer-to-peer platform that helps match borrowers and lenders using structured requests, subscription access and responsible communication."
>
  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container hero-inner">
      <h1 class="hero-title">
        Structured borrowing and lending requests. Paid access to a clearer peer-to-peer network.
      </h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">
        AmicBridge helps people who want to borrow and people who want to lend
        connect through structured requests. Users submit the details, we review
        for clarity and consistency, and subscribers can access aligned profiles
        to communicate directly. All agreements and transfers happen between users.
      </p>

      <div class="hero-buttons">
        <a href="#borrow" class="btn btn-primary">Request a loan</a>
        <a href="#lend" class="btn btn-secondary">Offer lending</a>
      </div>

      <p class="hero-note">
        Important: Paying for access does not guarantee any match, loan, income or result.
        Lending, borrowing and investing always involve risk, including the loss of money.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- MISSION -->
  <section id="mission" class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Mission & purpose</h2>
      <p class="section-lead">
        The mission of AmicBridge is to bring order and clarity to peer-to-peer finance.
        Borrowers explain their needs in a structured way. Lenders describe their capacity
        and conditions. AmicBridge stands in the middle with a transparent, paid-access
        model instead of hidden incentives.
      </p>

      <ul class="bridge-list">
        <li>Cyprus-based peer-to-peer request and matching platform</li>
        <li>Borrow, lend and request strategy using structured forms</li>
        <li>No custody of funds or crypto – users move money themselves</li>
        <li>Paid subscription to access matched borrower/lender profiles</li>
        <li>No promises of profit, matches, or repayment</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
  <section id="how" class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">How AmicBridge works</h2>
      <div class="how-grid">
        <div class="how-step">
          <span class="how-number">1</span>
          <div>
            <h3>Submit a structured request</h3>
            <p>
              Borrowers, lenders and strategy clients fill out forms with amount,
              asset type, timing, purpose and expectations. Submissions are stored
              for potential alignment.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="how-step">
          <span class="how-number">2</span>
          <div>
            <h3>Clarity review</h3>
            <p>
              AmicBridge reviews information for clarity and internal consistency.
              This does not guarantee reliability or creditworthiness, but it helps
              remove unclear or incomplete entries.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="how-step">
          <span class="how-number">3</span>
          <div>
            <h3>Subscriber access & contact</h3>
            <p>
              Users who pay the monthly subscription can access aligned profiles and
              decide who to contact. Agreements, checks and transfers remain the
              responsibility of the people involved.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TRUST -->
  <section id="trust" class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Trust principles</h2>
      <div class="principles-grid">
        <div class="principle-card">
          <h3>Structured information</h3>
          <p>
            Requests follow a standard structure so lenders and borrowers see the
            same type of information every time.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="principle-card">
          <h3>Identity context</h3>
          <p>
            Basic identity details are requested to reduce anonymous misuse. This is
            not a guarantee of financial strength or honesty.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="principle-card">
          <h3>Risk visibility</h3>
          <p>
            We highlight that peer-to-peer finance always has risk. Subscription
            fees do not remove risk or create guarantees.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="principle-card">
          <h3>No fund custody</h3>
          <p>
            AmicBridge does not hold money or crypto. Users transfer funds using
            their own bank or wallet channels.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- BORROW -->
  <section id="borrow" class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Request a loan</h2>
      <p class="section-lead">
        Describe clearly how much you need, in which asset, for how long, and why.
        Submitting a request is free. Access to potential lenders is part of the
        subscription.
      </p>

      <!-- BORROW FORM: SENDS EMAIL VIA FORMSPREE -->
      <form
        class="form"
        action="https://formspree.io/f/YOUR_FORMSPREE_BORROW_URL"
        method="POST"
      >
        <input type="hidden" name="_subject" value="New BORROW request on AmicBridge" />

        <label>
          Full name
          <input type="text" name="full_name" required />
        </label>

        <label>
          Email
          <input type="email" name="email" required />
        </label>

        <div class="form-row">
          <label>
            Amount
            <input type="number" name="amount" min="1" required />
          </label>
          <label>
            Asset
            <select name="asset">
              <option>EUR</option>
              <option>USD</option>
              <option>NOK</option>
              <option>BTC</option>
              <option>ETH</option>
              <option>USDT</option>
            </select>
          </label>
        </div>

        <label>
          Duration
          <select name="duration">
            <option>Up to 6 months</option>
            <option>Up to 12 months</option>
            <option>Up to 24 months</option>
            <option>Up to 36 months</option>
          </select>
        </label>

        <label>
          Max annual interest you can accept
          <input type="number" name="max_interest" min="1" max="40" />
        </label>

        <label>
          Purpose and repayment plan
          <textarea name="purpose" rows="3"></textarea>
        </label>

        <button class="btn btn-primary btn-full">Submit loan request</button>

        <p class="card-note">
          This form collects information only. No loan is created until you and a
          lender separately agree on terms.
        </p>
      </form>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- LEND -->
  <section id="lend" class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Offer lending</h2>
      <p class="section-lead">
        Explain what you are willing to lend, under which conditions, and what type
        of borrowers you prefer. Submitting your profile is free. Access to borrower
        profiles and contact is part of the subscription.
      </p>

      <!-- LEND FORM: SENDS EMAIL VIA FORMSPREE -->
      <form
        class="form"
        action="https://formspree.io/f/YOUR_FORMSPREE_LEND_URL"
        method="POST"
      >
        <input type="hidden" name="_subject" value="New LEND offer on AmicBridge" />

        <label>
          Full name
          <input type="text" name="full_name" required />
        </label>

        <label>
          Email
          <input type="email" name="email" required />
        </label>

        <div class="form-row">
          <label>
            Amount to lend
            <input type="number" name="amount" min="1" required />
          </label>
          <label>
            Asset
            <select name="asset">
              <option>EUR</option>
              <option>USD</option>
              <option>NOK</option>
              <option>BTC</option>
              <option>ETH</option>
              <option>USDT</option>
            </select>
          </label>
        </div>

        <label>
          Target annual interest
          <input type="number" name="target_interest" min="1" max="40" />
        </label>

        <label>
          Preferred borrower profile
          <textarea name="preferred_borrower" rows="3"></textarea>
        </label>

        <button class="btn btn-secondary btn-full">Submit lending profile</button>

        <p class="card-note">
          Lending is risky. Even with structured information, borrowers may fail to
          repay. Never lend more than you can afford to lose.
        </p>
      </form>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- STRATEGY -->
  <section id="strategy" class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Investment strategy requests</h2>
      <p class="section-lead">
        Submit a request for investment strategy ideas, including your budget for
        advice, risk tolerance and goals. Responses, if any, are not guaranteed
        performance.
      </p>

      <!-- STRATEGY FORM: SENDS EMAIL VIA FORMSPREE -->
      <form
        class="form"
        action="https://formspree.io/f/YOUR_FORMSPREE_STRATEGY_URL"
        method="POST"
      >
        <input type="hidden" name="_subject" value="New STRATEGY request on AmicBridge" />

        <label>
          Full name
          <input type="text" name="full_name" required />
        </label>

        <label>
          Email
          <input type="email" name="email" required />
        </label>

        <label>
          Budget for strategy service (EUR equivalent)
          <input type="number" name="budget" min="1" required />
        </label>

        <label>
          Goal
          <textarea name="goal" rows="3"></textarea>
        </label>

        <label>
          What can you invest in?
          <textarea name="assets" rows="2"></textarea>
        </label>

        <button class="btn btn-primary btn-full">Submit strategy request</button>

        <p class="card-note">
          Any ideas or strategies shared are informational only and cannot promise
          returns or prevent loss.
        </p>
      </form>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PRICING SUMMARY -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Subscription access</h2>
      <p class="section-lead">
        Submitting loan and lending requests is free. To access aligned profiles and
        contact details, users can subscribe to the AmicBridge access plan.
      </p>

      <div class="form" style="max-width: 480px;">
        <h3 style="margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">AmicBridge Access Plan</h3>
        <p style="margin:0 0 0.8rem;color:#555;">
          For borrowers and lenders who want access to matched profiles and direct
          contact options.
        </p>

        <p style="font-size:1.4rem;font-weight:600;margin:0 0 0.3rem;">
          €120 / month
        </p>
        <ul class="bridge-list" style="margin-top:0.6rem;">
          <li>Access to compatible borrower/lender profiles</li>
          <li>Ability to contact other users directly</li>
          <li>Structured information instead of unfiltered messages</li>
          <li>Support and clarification on how the platform works</li>
        </ul>

        <p class="card-note">
          The subscription fee grants access to the platform’s matching environment.
          It does not guarantee any match, loan, return, profit or repayment.
        </p>

        <a href="/access" class="btn btn-primary btn-full">
          Learn more &amp; subscription details
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- LOGIN -->
  <section id="login" class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Sign in</h2>
      <p class="section-lead">
        Once authentication and billing are connected, subscribers will be able to
        sign in to access the matching environment and manage their requests.
      </p>

      <form class="form">
        <label>
          Email
          <input type="email" name="login_email" required />
        </label>
        <label>
          Password
          <input type="password" name="login_password" required />
        </label>
        <button class="btn btn-primary btn-full">Sign in</button>
        <p class="card-note">
          This is a design placeholder. Real sign-in must be implemented with secure
          authentication and subscription validation.
        </p>
      </form>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- REGISTER -->
  <section id="register" class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Create an account</h2>
      <p class="section-lead">
        Creating an account links your requests to your identity. Subscription is
        required to access other users’ profiles and matches.
      </p>

      <form class="form">
        <label>
          Full name
          <input type="text" name="reg_full_name" required />
        </label>
        <label>
          Email
          <input type="email" name="reg_email" required />
        </label>
        <label>
          Password
          <input type="password" name="reg_password" required />
        </label>
        <label>
          Country of residence
          <input type="text" name="reg_country" required />
        </label>
        <label>
          Profile type
          <select name="reg_profile_type">
            <option>Borrower</option>
            <option>Lender</option>
            <option>Both</option>
          </select>
        </label>

        <button class="btn btn-secondary btn-full">Create account</button>

        <p class="card-note">
          Account creation does not imply background approval or any guarantee of
          successful lending or borrowing. Subscription and verification processes
          must be implemented on the backend.
        </p>
      </form>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CONTACT -->
  <section id="contact" class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Contact</h2>
      <p class="section-lead">
        For questions about the platform design, subscription model or future
        development, you can contact the founder directly or send a message using
        the form below.
      </p>

      <!-- CONTACT FORM: SENDS EMAIL VIA FORMSPREE -->
      <form
        class="form"
        action="https://formspree.io/f/YOUR_FORMSPREE_CONTACT_URL"
        method="POST"
      >
        <input type="hidden" name="_subject" value="New CONTACT message on AmicBridge" />

        <label>
          Your name
          <input type="text" name="name" required />
        </label>

        <label>
          Your email
          <input type="email" name="email" required />
        </label>

        <label>
          Message
          <textarea name="message" rows="4"></textarea>
        </label>

        <button class="btn btn-primary btn-full">Send message</button>

        <p class="card-note">
          For security, do not send passwords, card numbers or private keys.
        </p>
      </form>

      <div class="contact-card" style="margin-top:1.5rem;">
        <p><strong>CEO:</strong> Robert</p>
        <p>
          <strong>Email:</strong>
          <a href="mailto:Robertamicolsen@gmail.com">Robertamicolsen@gmail.com</a>
        </p>
        <p class="card-note">
          Direct email is available for important questions and partnership discussions.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
